sentences: Maëlle Pistoia  (born 4 January 2001), better known as simply Maëlle  is a French singer.

Born in January 2001, Maëlle Pistoia is from Tournus in the department of Saône-et-Loire, Burgundy.

sentences: Maëlle's musical career started in 2017, when she submitted a video audition for the seventh edition of the French version of The Voice and became a contestant.
